textAnnotations.description:
As he swung
her on to the floor Gay saw Gavin
and Simone go through the doirway that led
down to the beach. Gay closed her eyes for a
moment in disgust. She was fully aware that Gavin
would make love to the French girl on the sandsı
and no doubt he would come back soon and
after Simone had left expect her to accept his
lisses on
the
back to the hatel
way
